{"word":"Onyx","slug":"onyx","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Onyx</b> Precious stone<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=28&verse=16'>Job 28:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=28&verse=13'>Eze 28:13</a><br/> Used in erecting the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=2'>1Ch 29:2</a><br/> Seen in the foundations of the city of the New Jerusalem in John's apocalyptic vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=21&verse=20'>Rev 21:20</a><br/> Exported from Havilah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=12'>Gen 2:12</a><br/> Used in the breastplate<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=12'>Exo 28:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=20'>Exo 28:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=6'>Exo 39:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=13'>Exo 39:13</a><br/> Contributed by Israelites for the priests' garments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=7'>Exo 25:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=9'>Exo 35:9</a>"}]}